Package: lingglosses
Type: Package
Title: Linguistic Examples and Abbreviation Lists Generation
Version: 0.0.2
Depends: R (>= 3.5.0)
Authors@R: person("George", "Moroz",
                  role = c("aut", "cre"),
                  email = "agricolamz@gmail.com",
                  comment = c(ORCID="0000-0003-1990-6083"))
Maintainer: George Moroz <agricolamz@gmail.com>
Description: 'lingglosses' helps to render glossed linguistic examples in html
    rmarkdown documents and then semi-automatically compiles the glosses list at
    the end of the document. It also provides a database of linguistic glosses.
License: GPL (>= 3)
